<IW:HTML4:"interact/forms.html#adef-method">
-- [CITE[17.13.1 Form submission method]]
<IW:HTML4:"interact/forms.html#idx-form-8">

[21]
HTML 4 DTD [[注釈]] (参考) には
[Q[HTTP method used to submit the form]]
と説明があります。

